claim.claim-text:
1. A membrane assembly comprising:
an inorganic filtering membrane;
an intermediate layer comprising silicon dioxide or silicon nitride, wherein the filtering membrane is disposed on a surface of the intermediate layer; and an anodized substrate comprising a plurality of macropores, wherein another surface of the intermediate layer is coupled to a first surface of the anodized substrate, wherein at least a portion of a second surface of the anodized substrate comprises a guiding pattern having a plurality of pre-patterned pores, and wherein the first and second surfaces are disposed opposite each other.
